                    "sections": [
                        {
                            "type": "nodes.branchSection",
                            "expression": {
                                "type": "expressions.hasActiveQuest",
                                "propId": "6fdd5328-909a-40a3-8b6a-5d9feae40b4d",
                                "sceneId": "e8520824-d970-4c6e-8aec-6c308c8846ab",
                                "questStatus": "0"
                            },
                            "nodes": [
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.quests",
                                    "id": "adadd765-6873-4d8b-9b8a-d422c201584a",
                                    "sceneId": "e8520824-d970-4c6e-8aec-6c308c8846ab",
                                    "propId": "6fdd5328-909a-40a3-8b6a-5d9feae40b4d",
                                    "target": "2",
                                    "notify": true
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "7148a6ca-0f1d-460c-aeda-8653058b2af2",
                                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "Welcome back, Shawn. We hoped that you would again join us.",
                                    "emotion": "1",
                                    "emotion2": "4",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                }
                            ]
                        }
                    ]
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.changeReputation",
                    "id": "24e812b5-4553-4289-a132-3474195f7349",
                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                    "amount": "2",
                    "change": "1",
                    "notify": true
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "39822c6a-4936-4cc3-9780-ce76e44a8ebe",
                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "This lesson is centered upon Enchantment and Alchemy. You have already experienced the Aspect of Enchantment when you created runestones - you imbued an object with magical energy and focus.",
                    "emotion": "0",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "b6c0dabd-22e4-4a07-b3b0-cf15b28dc618",
                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "That is the nature of Enchantment. It is the method by which an Enchanter creates magic items. It is limited by the nature of the object upon which the spell is cast.",
                    "emotion": "0",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "b2377b3d-460c-46fd-b5b8-6187a5b18efb",
                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "If the object itself is non-magical, the Enchantment will be temporary at best. Some objects, such as iron, cannot be enchanted.",
                    "emotion": "0",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "f01d3acd-f701-4ede-b5fd-2781179d7951",
                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "Then there are objects that readily accept magical spells like the clay that we use to create runestones. The clay is readily suffused with magic. Nevertheless, the clay is in and of itself still clay.",
                    "emotion": "0",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "70d6f78a-d124-4656-acc0-f5ba40dc53cf",
                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "Alchemy is the Aspect of transformation. An Alchemist is one who seeks to transmute an object from one substance to another.",
                    "emotion": "0",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "753c980a-ff22-4867-a906-0bda6b022d16",
                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "Are there any questions or comments before we address this topic further?",
                    "emotion": "0",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "id": "9a6efefc-3101-47ad-9ca6-dfaf7e83d301",
                    "type": "nodes.improveSkill",
                    "skill": "Magic",
                    "amount": "2",
                    "notify": true
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.showMenu",
                    "id": "ea99cd7e-a915-42ad-a6c0-14cdb358ede9",
                    "options": [
                        {
                            "type": "options.text",
                            "id": "4bc0e5cd-1923-4919-bb62-663e11013bdb",
                            "text": "Ask About Enchanters",
                            "nodes": [
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "a8adfb1d-86f5-4082-a7c7-c22a906a0a4d",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "text": "So... since we have been enchanting runestones, does that make us Enchanters?",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "cf5903da-1825-42f5-8a7d-ae031443124b",
                                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "If you were a Wizard who specialized in enchantment, you would be considered to be an Enchanter. As a Magic User, no, unless you chose to devote your life to the craft.",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "a5f75b5d-9fe2-40cf-ab68-a54fa95d973b",
                                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "I suspect that you have better things to do in your future than making runestones and minor magic items.",
                                    "emotion": "1",
                                    "emotion2": "1",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "id": "05a636f2-b4f1-4944-b61f-bc13afde0f21",
                                    "type": "nodes.skillBranch",
                                    "skill": "Smarts",
                                    "target": "58",
                                    "success": {
                                        "type": "nodes.block",
                                        "nodes": []
                                    },
                                    "failure": {
                                        "type": "nodes.block",
                                        "nodes": []
                                    },
                                    "notify": true
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.changeReputation",
                                    "id": "66ccdd56-e686-4833-a5a1-76680d98dd6c",
                                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "amount": "2",
                                    "change": "1",
                                    "notify": true
                                }
                            ],
                            "expression": null,
                            "ignoreChildAvailability": false,
                            "minutes": "5",
                            "ExitMenu": true
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "options.text",
                            "id": "0eebdd7d-8496-4658-b4a6-6f756a0931e4",
                            "text": "Ask About Professor Featherstonehaugh",
                            "nodes": [
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "12462490-644c-4156-89e4-1ed0ea4260d3",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "text": "Since you taught us how to make runestones, does this mean that you are an Enchanter?",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "65595226-24ab-468a-8610-2bd5a0fb31d9",
                                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "At the moment, I am more of an instructor than a Wizard. However, as a Wizard, I have always been a generalist. I am fascinated by all studies of magic.",
                                    "emotion": "1",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "d9201c18-03bf-4334-89fe-c89b93efb0d0",
                                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "My Magister considered me to be a bit too much of a flibbertigibbet to specialize. Then again, he didn't think that I could be a Wizard either. I was quite pleased to prove him to be mistaken in my abilities.",
                                    "emotion": "1",
                                    "emotion2": "1",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "id": "41aba8d0-624d-4ab0-8ed1-a3247b056804",
                                    "type": "nodes.skillBranch",
                                    "skill": "Charm",
                                    "target": "58",
                                    "success": {
                                        "type": "nodes.block",
                                        "nodes": []
                                    },
                                    "failure": {
                                        "type": "nodes.block",
                                        "nodes": []
                                    },
                                    "notify": true
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.changeReputation",
                                    "id": "0844ed18-bb35-4c3f-8d82-b31586385110",
                                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "amount": "2",
                                    "change": "1",
                                    "notify": true
                                }
                            ],
                            "expression": null,
                            "ignoreChildAvailability": false,
                            "minutes": "6",
                            "ExitMenu": false
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "options.text",
                            "id": "f017ff12-b5ef-4318-9984-9efd8f2c6779",
                            "text": "Make a Joke About Alchemy",
                            "nodes": [
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "a1cca12d-6ffc-4c50-a0cf-57565c45dbfc",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "text": "Did you hear about the Alchemist who tried to bottle his own essence? - He made a flask of himself.",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "4",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "688f3b9f-c28d-49dd-93fa-efc6d0b63572",
                                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "I have no idea of what you are speaking.",
                                    "emotion": "3",
                                    "emotion2": "1",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "6d966222-0277-4779-811d-b0b194c8b30e",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "text": "He made a flask of... Eh, never mind.",
                                    "emotion": "1",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "id": "dfd45680-34a8-4a8b-b791-3e2df35657fe",
